Animation assignment:
Create a box and specify the color to be changed for every second.

<html>
<head>
    <style>
        div {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background-color: #BDB76B;
            animation-name: test;
            animation-duration:1s;
            animation-iteration-count: infinite;
            animation-delay: 2s;
        }



        /* Standard syntax */
        @keyframes test {
            0%   {background-color: #BDB76B;}
            25%  {background-color: #8B008B;}
            50%  {background-color: #556B2F;}
            100% {background-color: #FF8C00;}
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

